uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.triples

Class OTMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NMatcher
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.reason.OROntologyLinkedMatcher
        • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.triples.OTMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatcher

    public abstract class OTMatcher
extends OROntologyLinkedMatcher
    Extension of OROntologyLinkedMatcher that represents the instances via sets of triples in an RDF triple store, and the queries as SPARQL queries over that store. The store will be dynamically populated, and possibly created, on start-up, and emptied or removed on termination.

    This is an abstract class each of whose extensions will provide an implementation for a particular type of triple store.
